@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rozdkm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.exp(v2 + 0.83) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.57)))
    tmp = (0.30 - (v2 * (tmp + 0.31 * v0 + 0.84)))
    v0 = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.14 + v0 + 0.07) + 0.62))
    data[tid] = v0
